Description.DefaultText: Qwinn's Ultimate Dragon Age: Origins Fixpack, by Paul (Qwinn) Escalona. v3.5 Fixes over 850 bugs in base Dragon Age: Origins. Attempts to fix everything except combat mechanics and Awakening/DLC bugs. Compatible with mods that affect only those, as well as texture/morph mods. Enjoy!
